{"tid":762264,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"前AKB成員前田敦子閃婚！交往未滿半年昨登記","createTime":"2018-07-31T06:30:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-05T09:36:05.000Z","uid":3189,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"43db2fd9ccdf065cec495d134fdc6d06c08e687a","tid":762264,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T06:30:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180731/640_796dd8bb34050fc5f5e3aa8bd66629f5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180731%2F640_796dd8bb34050fc5f5e3aa8bd66629f5.jpg&h=a8288fef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前田敦子（右）和勝地涼因合作《全力青蛙》結緣。翻攝畫面<br />\n<br />\n日本國民女團「AKB48」27歲前人氣成員前田敦子2012年退團後轉型演員，她今年5月被爆與31歲男星勝地涼熱戀ing，交往還不到半年，今《日本體育報》報導2人已在昨天登記結婚。報導指出，敦子目前並沒有懷孕，2人稍早發出聯合聲明證實婚訊，內容提及「被雙方的個性所吸引，以結婚為前提展開交往」，也表示：「雖然我們兩個都有未成熟之處，但會一起共築笑容不絕的開朗家庭。今後我們會互相扶持，並認真對待每一份接到的工作繼續努力。」<br />\n <br />\n敦子和勝地2015年因合作日劇《全力青蛙》而結識，去年9月因電影《食女子》（暫譯）合作拉近距離，今年春天展開交往，5月八卦周刊爆初2人拍拖消息時，雙方都沒有否認戀情。（王怡文／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180731/1401767/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180731%2F1401767%2F&d=1InRUhZWaBoppC7aDIOFyTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=4b94f1de\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180731%2F1401767%2F&h=daf0f1de\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180731/1401767/</a>"},{"pid":"2e03b5a2a69c94a0c4ad0c33b8f0d72db5b25d91","tid":762264,"uid":35014,"like":7,"dislike":37,"score":-30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T06:34:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ec51ff6a1240eb6adbdfa2e38d8d3cf365711e23","tid":762264,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T08:43:26.000Z","msg":"幾靚仔"},{"pid":"ef590b14d92034f8373bce8ac98e692a9f0fb203","tid":762264,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31